Field.name: TimeStamp
Field.description: Unix Epoch UTS time (no GMT offset added)

Field.name: Switches
Field.description: switch summary where SW1 = LSB and SW5=bit5

Field.name: Relay
Field.description: Uint8 bitmap. $ least significant bits represent the current state of the output relay drives on the GNX5/10

Field.name: IBID
Field.description: Added in firmware .76 (March 2012) 4 bytes showing the 4 least significant bytes of the ibutton, as read on the ibutton, not including the 01 ibutton type.

Field.name: FMI
Field.description: FMI status 70||198 is On else Off

Field.name: TemperatureSensors
Field.description: 4 * int16. This column is a summary of the four external 1 wire tempsensors (as shown in DIAG 1WIRE response)
